Upgrade 5 — Distortion and Omission Ledger

Every frame leaves something out.

LTI 3.0 logs:
	•	what this trajectory illuminated
	•	what it hid
	•	what got flattened
	•	what became harder to say after lock

This prevents false confidence in any one framing.

